{"tid":1980353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盲醫林順潮品嚐過人民幣後返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2020-04-20T04:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T10:32:11.000Z","uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b77c7b3402a3fb8086f1f66313b81228657d814c","tid":1980353,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"愛共就是生財工具，人格？良知？誠信？ 值幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過牠的子女全部入藉左那裡？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRrHCeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRrHCeT.jpg&h=6841350a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb9dd39a7799b50825097c32722b9f475fa6af1a","tid":1980353,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2bd5f73320ed30e403d0243d583b4458c2818d","tid":1980353,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"在科學共產主義（馬克思主義以及其各流派）的生產方式理論中，它在發展上分三個階段：<br />\n<br />\n初級階段是一個社會由原始邁向封建，再邁向資本主義，之後該社會在階級矛盾困境中覺醒開始社會主義，即沒收私有生產資料為國有化並為公有制社會的起步鋪墊基礎；<br />\n<br />\n中期階段是公有制社會戰勝私有制世界的階段，由於體現生產按比例協調發展的優勢，馬克思稱為社會主義優越性[4]，能夠極大地吸引了私有制社會裏的廣大中下層人民，使社會主義能夠在私有制世界的包圍圈裏得到蔓延與擴展不斷突破、戰勝後最終公有制世界完全代替私有制世界；<br />\n<br />\n高級階段是在社會主義更加穩定、科技更高的基礎上開始步入社會主義高級階段，生產方式理論的最後型態即邁入共產主義社會階段，當公有制世界得到持續穩定的發展後，共產自由世界形成雛形，那時世界上已經不再有階級、國家和政府，政府的職能幾乎被下降到社會的各領域裏。通常所說的共產主義理想指最後的高級階段，也就是共產主義的自由世界。[5] <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4496f333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n佢呢間眼科醫院應該唔收錢先係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則就係資本主義走狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb63109c99a6304165d690794501b5a0a414161b","tid":1980353,"uid":129134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:16:21.000Z","msg":"之前有手足瞓喺醫院，比人爆晒個人資料出嚟<br />\n行內醫生個個都指係林順潮爆的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a10b488730d68078f7461b596cc495b14e815f8","tid":1980353,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb63109c99a6304165d690794501b5a0a414161b","tid":1980353,"uid":129134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:16:21.000Z","msg":"之前有手足瞓喺醫院，比人爆晒個人資料出嚟<br />\n行內醫生個個都指係林順潮爆的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"又衰十一？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}